name: Verify error message for invalid code on Try Editor
fullName: Arrays: Verify error message for invalid code on Try Editor

steps.name: Given  The user is logged with valid credential and the user is on the Home page
When  The user clicks the Get Started button in Array Panel
Then  The user should be navigated to the Array page
Given  The user is on the tryEditor page of Array in python
When  The user clicks Run button with invalid code from sheetname "tryEditorCode" and row 1 for Arrays in Python page
Then  The user should be able to see an error message in alert window
